          </div>`;
        if (state.mines.includes('money') || state.mines.includes('visibility')) {
          warnEl.innerHTML = `<div class="lc-warning-card"><p>A money ceiling or fear of visibility will stall your acquisition before the strategy gets a chance to work. This is the first block to address, not the last.</p></div>`;
